### 1. 测试新增用户 (POST 请求，带 JSON 数据)
POST http://localhost:8085/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "new_student",
  "password": "123",
  "realName": "新同学",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 2. 测试根据 ID 查询用户 (GET 请求)
GET http://localhost:8085/user/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. 测试根据用户名查询 (GET 请求)
GET http://localhost:8085/user/username/admin
Accept: application/json

### 4. 测试查询所有教师 (GET 请求)
GET http://localhost:8085/user/teachers
Accept: application/json

### 5. 测试更新用户 (PUT 请求，修改之前添加的 new_student)
PUT http://localhost:8085/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 8,
  "password": "456",
  "realName": "新同学(已修改)",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 6. 测试删除用户 (DELETE 请求)
DELETE http://localhost:8085/user/8